div.p: On Enter Pending: • Queue sync operation • Validate Git source • Check authentication • Initialize sync context
During InProgress: • Fetch manifests from Git • Compare desired vs current state • Apply resource changes • Handle dependencies • Update sync status
On Success: • Update last sync timestamp • Record applied revision • Clear error conditions • Trigger health checks
On Failure: • Log error details • Increment retry counter • Set backoff timer • Preserve partial state • Notify operators
